title: Swedish Massage
description: A relaxing massage therapy session using gentle but firm pressure to promote relaxation, ease muscle tension, and create other health benefits.

title: Deep Tissue Massage
description: A type of massage aimed at the deeper tissue structures of the muscle and fascia, also called connective tissue.

title: Hot Stone Massage
description: A specialty massage where smooth, heated stones are used by placing them on the body while they massage other parts of the body.

title: Aromatherapy Massage
description: Massage therapy with essential oils added to the massage oil, inhaled through the air and absorbed through the skin.

title: Reflexology
description: A system of massage used to relieve tension and treat illness, based on the theory that there are reflex points on the feet, hands, and head linked to every part of the body.

title: Sports Massage
description: A form of bodywork geared towards participants in athletics and designed to help prevent injuries, to prepare the body for athletic activity and maintain it in optimal condition.
